OL,4,G1800FRamsay's Hotel Hell
OL,5,     GVerindar runs her place like a
OL,6,     Gtyrant. Her employees are fed up
OL,7,     Gwith staying silent. So Gordon
OL,8,     Gtries to sprinkle his magic.
OL,9,     GHopefully the hotel won't stay so
OL,10,     Gtragic. _WorldPoetryDay
OL,11,G1900FRamsay's Hotel Hell
OL,12,     GIf you're looking for a place to
OL,13,     Gsleep, at this resort you won't
OL,14,     Gget a peep. In these not-so-great
OL,15,     Gdigs, Brian hosts late-night
OL,16,     Ggigs. And his service would make
OL,17,     Gyou weep. _WorldPoetryDay
